ite running. Specific affiliate programs we participate in will be listed here once they are active.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Earning a commission does not change which products appear on this site or where they rank. We list products based on what we think fits a given shopper, not based on which one pays us more. If a product is a poor fit for a category, we don't include it just because the affiliate payout would be higher.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"We are not the manufacturer or seller of any product listed. For order questions, returns, or warranty support, please go directly to the retailer where you purchased.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-sm text-slate-600\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"This disclosure is provided in accordance with the U.S. Federal Trade Commission's guidance on endorsements and testimonials.\\\"}]]}]]}]}]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"9:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"pb-12\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"container-shell\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"card p-6 sm:p-10\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-3xl\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Who runs this site\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-4 space-y-4 text-base leading-8 text-slate-700\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Interactive Pet Marketplace is curated and researched by\\\",\\\" \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Tim Thomasson\\\"}],\\\". Product research, privacy reviews, and editorial decisions are made by a single person — not an anonymous team or an AI content pipeline. Every product on this site has been chosen, reviewed, and written about by hand.\\\"]}]}]]}