.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4 text-base leading-7 text-slate-700\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"There are a lot of interactive pets on the market, and they get marketed as the answer to very different needs — companionship for a parent living alone, a calming presence for someone with dementia, a novelty gift, or a kid's first taste of a \\\"pet.\\\" Lumping them all together makes choosing harder, not easier.\"}],\"$L5\"]}]]}]}]}],\"$L6\",\"$L7\",\"$L8\",\"$L9\",\"$La\"]}],null,\"$Lb\"]}],{},null,false,null]},null,false,\"$@c\"]},null,false,null],\"$Ld\",false]],\"m\":\"$undefined\",\"G\":[\"$e\",[]],\"S\":true,\"h\":null,\"s\":\"$undefined\",\"l\":\"$undefined\",\"p\":\"$undefined\",\"d\":\"$undefined\",\"b\":\"acFLag9weJPW7aMMY7VNM\"}\nf:I[8500,[\"756\",\"static/chunks/756-98a13f2d10827e2b.js\",\"220\",\"static/chunks/app/about/page-1f374704d40e8be0.js\"],\"\"]\n10:I[484,[],\"OutletBoundary\"]\n11:\"$Sreact.suspense\"\n14:I[484,[],\"ViewportBoundary\"]\n16:I[484,[],\"MetadataBoundary\"]\n5:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"The team behind Interactive Pet Marketplace organizes products by who they're best for and what they actually do, so you can narrow things down quickly. We focus on plushy companions, AI & robotic pets, and senior-friendly options — the categories where buyers most often tell us they feel overwhelmed.\"}]\n6:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"pb-12\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"container-shell\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"card p-6 sm:p-10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"eyebrow\",\"children\":\"How we choose what to list\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-3xl\",\"children\":\"Our standards for product information.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Verified data only\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\",\"children\":\"Specs, ratings, review counts, and prices come from manufacturer pages or major retailers and are checked manually. If we can't verify a number, it doesn't go on the site.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Refreshed regularly\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\",\"children\":\"Prices and ratings drift over time. Higher-priced and popular products get checked more often than long-tail listings, and every product card reflects when the data was last verified.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"No copied reviews\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\",\"children\":\"We never reproduce customer review text from Amazon, the manufacturer, or anywhere else. Reviews belong to the people who wrote them. We link out instead.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Editorial highlights are ours\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\",\"children\":\"Where we add a short \\\"what makes this stand out\\\" note, that's our editorial voice — not a manufacturer claim. We try to be clear about which is which.\"}]]}]]}]]}]}]}]\n7:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"pb-12\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"container-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"eyebrow\",\"children\":\"Who this site is for\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-3xl\",\"children\":\"We organize the site around shoppers, not categories.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"Seniors and their families\",{\"className\":\"rounded-3xl border border-trust-200 bg-trust-50 p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-semibold text-trust-900\",\"children\":\"Seniors and their families\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\",\"children\":\"Calmer choices with simple interaction, designed for comfort over complexity.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Kids and families\",{\"className\":\"rounded-3xl border border-trust-200 bg-trust-50 p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-semibold text-trust-900\",\"children\":\"Kids and families\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\",\"children\":\"Playful options built for novelty, learning, and everyday entertainment.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Gift buyers\",{\"className\":\"rounded-3xl border border-trust-200 bg-trust-50 p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-semibold text-trust-900\",\"children\":\"Gift buyers\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\",\"children\":\"Friendly picks with broad appeal that don't require setup expertise.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Premium shoppers\",{\"className\":\"rounded-3xl border border-trust-200 bg-trust-50 p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-semibold text-trust-900\",\"children\":\"Premium shoppers\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\",\"children\":\"Higher-end robotic pets with more advanced sensors and movement.\"}]]}]]}]]}]}]\n8:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"pb-12\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"container-shell\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"id\":\"affiliate-disclosure\",\"className\":\"rounded-3xl border-2 border-trust-300 bg-trust-50 p-6 sm:p-10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"eyebrow\",\"children\":\"Affiliate disclosure\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-trust-900 sm:text-3xl\",\"children\":\"How we make money — in plain language.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-5 space-y-4 text-base leading-7 text-slate-700\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Interactive Pet Marketplace may participate in affiliate programs. If you click a \\\"View Details\\\" or product link on this site and go on to buy, we may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. Any commissions help fund the time it takes to research products, verify prices, and keep the site running. Specific affiliate programs we participate in will be listed here once they are active.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Earning a commission does not change which products appear on this site or where they rank. We list products based on what we think fits a given shopper, not based on which one pays us more. If a product is a poor fit for a category, we don't include it just because the affiliate payout would be higher.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"We are not the manufacturer or seller of any product listed. For order questions, returns, or warranty support, please go directly to the retailer where you purchased.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-slate-600\",\"children\":\"This disclosure is provided in accordance with the U.S. Federal Trade Commission's guidance on endorsements and testimonials.\"}]]}]]}]}]}]\n9:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"pb-12\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"container-shell\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"card p-6 sm:p-10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-3xl\",\"children\":\"Who runs this site\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-4 text-base leading-8 text-slate-700\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"Interactive Pet Marketplace is curated and researched by\",\" \",[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Tim Thomasson\"}],\". Product research, privacy reviews, and editorial decisions are made by a single person — not an anonymous team or an AI content pipeline. Every product on this site has been chosen, reviewed, and written about by hand.\"]}]}]]}]}]}]\na:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"pb-16 sm:pb-20\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"container-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"card p-6 sm:p-10 text-center\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-3xl\",\"children\":\"Have any questions or suggestions?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-base leading-7 text-slate-700\",\"children\":\"Whether you're trying to decide between two products, want to suggest a pet we should review, or noticed something on the site that doesn't look right — we'd like to hear from you.\"}],[\"$\",\"$Lf\",null,{\"href\":\"/contact\",\"className\":\"btn-primary mt-6 inline-flex\",\"children\":\"Contact us\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-8 text-center\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs text-slate-500 sm:text-sm\",\"children\":[\"Last updated: \",[\"$\",\"time\",null,{\"dateTime\":\"2026-05-17\",\"children\":\"2026-05-17\"}]]}]}]]}]}]\nb:[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$11\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@12\"}]}]\n13:[]\nc:\"$W13\"\nd:[\"$\",\"$1\",\"h\",{\"children\":[null,[\"$\",\"$L14\",null,{\"children\":\"$L15\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"hidden\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L16\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$11\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.Metadata\",\"children\":\"$L17\"}]}]}],null]}]\n15:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width,